📊 Key Data Fields:
Trip ID – Unique identifier for each trip
Pickup Date – Date of the ride
Vehicle Type – UberX, Uber Black, Uber Comfort, UberXL, Uber Green
Payment Type – Uber Pay, Cash
Passenger Count – Number of passengers per trip
Total Trip Distance – Distance covered in miles
Total Booking Value – Fare amount per trip
Pickup Location – Location ID of pickup
Hour Information – Time-based trip tracking
📈 Dashboard Features:
Tabular View: Displays complete trip-level data in a structured format
Data Filtering: Users can scroll and analyze specific trips easily
Vehicle Insights: Compare performance across different vehicle types
Payment Analysis: Understand usage of cash vs digital payments
Passenger Trends: Identify ride-sharing patterns (single vs multiple passengers)
Distance & Fare Analysis: Track how distance impacts booking value
